	1.	gets an OAuth token
	2.	POSTs the email payload
	3.	polls the delivery status until COMPLETED/ERROR (or times out)

Below is a compact, production-friendly implementation using RestTemplate (what you already have). It keeps the code in one service class, with clear error handling and comments. No caching (you can add it later by memoizing the token + expires_at).

